question.title: query all contacts in ContentResolver resolved in ANR

node.contents: I encountered in an annoying bug, that happens only on Nexus 4. Everytime, when I'm going through all the contacts of the device I'm getting ANR. Obviously, first thing that I did is to go through the traces.txt in order to find if there were deadlock or starvation and there weren't.
